name: Tape Gag
description:
v1.0
A simple LoRA model that allows you to put a tape gag on your character. Works with LoRA character models. The screenshots (if they pass moderation) show characters such as Lucy from Edgerunners, Prinz Eugen from Azure Lane and Marikawa Shizuka from High School of Dead.

Tips: scale - 1 will be good
Training model: NAI
Used to generation model: AOM3
Keywords: tape gag

If you want to help me with learning how to create LoRA models, or learn to create models with me - please join my server in discord, my goal is to create a friendly community that will help each other to achieve high quality training for LoRA models.
discord.gg/vmVzJQEhqy

If u know how to improve model, let me know
